  "summary": "Tyler Black is an offensive-minded prospect known for elite plate discipline and high on-base ability, combined with plus speed. While he makes consistent contact, his power is projected to be modest. He is a versatile defender, having played second base, third base, and outfield, but his below-average arm strength and lack of a true defensive home are concerns. Injuries have impacted his development, and he is working to establish a consistent role in the majors. He debuted in MLB in April 2024 but has had brief call-ups and was optioned to Triple-A Nashville in March 2026.",
